  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of the reliability of the PEPPER robot in assisting and recording the parameters&#xD;
      of a TM6. Patients referred to the EFRED service for the performance of a 6MWT will be&#xD;
      assisted during their test by the PEPPER robot. The PEPPER robot will also collect the&#xD;
      parameters of the 6MWT and produce a report. The EFRED service technician will remain present&#xD;
      during the 6MWT and will take note of the test parameters. An evaluation of patient&#xD;
      satisfaction with the assistance of the Robot Pepper in the realization of the 6MWT will also&#xD;
      be carried out.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
